    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Congratulations! If you are reading this page, it means that your blog
installation was successful.</p>

<!-- more -->


<h2>Want to write some articles?</h2>

<p>Copy the file <code>2014-03-09-your-first-post.markdown</code>, update the
title, date and categories in the header, and start writing!</p>

<p>I recommend <a href="http://www.markdownpad.com/">MarkdownPad</a> for editing.
You should read up on <a href="http://daringfireball.net/projects/markdown/syntax">Markdown
Syntax</a> to learn
about the basic formatting that this software supports.</p>
